    "body": "I've investigated several ways how we can go with this issue, and decided to use dns and ens names for granting permissions, full url doesn't work because dapps have several pages and they can request permissions on the first page and use web3 on the second page, and dapp will be broken, so we should give permission for all dapp pages, using dns name or ens name, if someone hosts several dapps on the same domain we can't do anything with it. We'll show domain to user, and he should decide if he wants to grant access to all dapps hosted on this domain or not",
